          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1659891233758-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain, then add the <strong>king prawns</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>grated ginger </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
